\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The South African College of Applied Psychology \'28SACAP\'29 is a private higher institution that has been accredited by the HEQC and registered by the Department of Higher Education and Training. The institution is currently offering a Diploma in Counselling Communication and a Graduate Diploma in Counselling.\line \line Please note\'3A SACAP has concurrently applied for an additional new site of delivery at the Johannesburg campus.\line \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
